data.description: Pine Trails – Nisswa is here!  This single-family home community with 45 homes is nestled between Downtown Nisswa (2 blocks), Nisswa Lake and Clark Lake.  Community features include a paddle board/canoe dock on Clark Lake, pavilion, playground, walking trails and abundant nature.  Community access to Paul Bunyan trail system, trails to Nisswa Lake, main street Nisswa, schools, library, parks….   Whether you are looking to paddle-board, bike, walk the dog, drop the boat into the Gull Lake chain or simply enjoying your new home, this community has it all. This model is the popular Retreat plan by Thomas Allen Homes built with all the popular upgrade options. Single family homes range from 2bd/1ba to 5bd/3ba homes: split level, one level, 1.5 story & our newest 2 story plans are all available.
